track.description:
So about a year ago, I got inspired to remix a song. Right from the jump I knew it was going to be an up hill battle taking on a truly iconic and timeless classic. As time went on, the project evolved from just a remix to a full on original interpretation. I eventually had the vocal re-sung, swapped out the famous melody for one I created and so on. The result is an original production I am beyond proud to have made & what is probably my best work to date.
